headline: Karen Fu,  Victor Alves
abstract: The couple met through a dating app in September 2015 in New York.
lead_paragraph: Karen Fu and Victor Alves were married Jan. 17 at San Francisco City Hall. Nancy Carlson, the deputy marriage commissioner, officiated. On April 11, Daniel Gelfarb, a friend of the groom, is to lead the couple in a second ceremony where they are to exchange vows at the Palms Hotel and Spa in Miami.
